+sub_section( 'Free theme available via WordPress repository' )
	p Use this procedure when you obtained the theme for free from <a href="https://profiles.wordpress.org/webmandesign#content-themes">WordPress themes repository</a>.

	ol
		li Log into your WordPress admin.

		li In WordPress admin navigate to #[+mark( 'nav', 'Appearance', 'Themes' )] and click the #[+mark( 'btn', 'Add New' )] button next to "Themes" page title.

		li On "Add Themes" screen use a search field to search for "#{config.name}".

		li Once you've found the theme in the search results list, click the #[+mark( 'btn', 'Install' )] button when hovering over the theme.

		li After the theme is installed, activate it by clicking the <strong>"Activate"</strong> link.

		li Now you can go to #[+mark( 'nav', 'Appearance', 'Welcome' )] page for information on how to set up your website (and the theme). Also, please <strong>pay special attention to your <a href="#image-sizes">website image sizes setup</a></strong>.
